<p><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong>1) Review the leadership levels above.</p>
<p>2) Then review specific area needs by exploring their Applications  pages found in the left navigation of this page.</p>
<p>3) Apply for the position.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><strong><a href="https://byui.qualtrics.com/SE/?SID=SV_5BVoPQHkqDIetTK"></a></strong></strong></p>
<p><em>Remember: Because each area of Activities is unique they will have differences in what they are looking for in Volunteers, Managers, Coordinators, Student Directors, and Area Directors. Be sure to look at their area needs </em><em>&nbsp;</em><em>before applying for that position.</em><em>&nbsp;</em></p>
